smul_eq:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
@[simp, to_additive]
theorem smul_eq (r : R) : «expr • » r y = unit :=
  rfl
#align smul_eq smul_eq
